===============================
Kestrel Jupyter Notebook Kernel
===============================

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/kestrel-lang
        :target: https://www.python.org/
        :alt: Python 3
        
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20style-black-000000.svg
